      "description": "$46,900 - Mint-condition car that presents exceptionally well inside and out, with a very clean body, paint, and interior and none of the noticeable wear you\u2019d expect on an average used vehicle. It has clearly been well cared for and should appeal to a buyer looking for a standout example that is ready to enjoy right away. Expect a highly presentable, turn-key car with strong overall cosmetics and condition.",
