    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Needs work and priced accordingly. This is a poor-condition vehicle best suited for a buyer looking for cheap transportation, a project, or something to repair. Expect significant cosmetic wear, noticeable age and use throughout, and a higher likelihood of mechanical issues or deferred maintenance. It is not a clean or trouble-free car, but for the right buyer who understands what they are getting, it could still be useful as basic transportation or a fixer-upper.",
