    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$35,500 - Good, honest classic with a clean presentation and the kind of well-cared-for feel that makes it easy to enjoy right away. It shows nicely overall, with solid paint, interior, and trim for a driver-quality example that has clearly been looked after. Not a concours car, but a very appealing, tidy classic that should make its next owner proud.",
