    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical entry point for a value-minded buyer seeking basic transportation or a worthwhile project. It shows clear signs of age and use, but it remains an appealing low-cost option for someone comfortable with a vehicle that has cosmetic and mechanical needs. Priced to reflect its condition, this is a budget buy with real potential for the right owner.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it starts, runs, and could make a great cheap commuter, first car, or project for someone handy. If you\u2019re after affordable wheels without spending a fortune, this one is worth a look. Priced to sell and ready to go.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong project or budget-driver opportunity with solid bones and a drivetrain that still delivers dependable pull. Starts, runs, and moves, with the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it appealing for someone who prefers wrench-friendly ownership over expensive complexity. Not a showroom piece, but it has honest character, usable road presence, and the right foundation for a restoration, commuter build, or parts-saving revival. If you want an affordable car with real potential and a platform worth improving, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Used and rough around the edges, but ready to go. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, lived-in character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still turns heads not because it\u2019s perfect, but because it has a story. It\u2019s a great fit for someone who wants an affordable driver, a hands-on project, or a practical set of wheels with real personality. If you enjoy bringing out the best in a vehicle and appreciate something with grit, charm, and plenty of potential, this one is easy to imagine making your own.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a straightforward option for buyers seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone comfortable with a well-used car, but it offers real value as an economical commuter, backup vehicle, or project opportunity. Priced to sell and represented honestly, this is a chance to secure affordable wheels without overpaying.",
      "price": 4895.0,
